Build An End User Profile


Use Primary Market Research to flesh out a detailed description of the end user

Customers typically consists of an END USER and DECISION-MAKING UNIT --
END USER - Individual who will use your product 
DECISION MAKING UNIT - Those who have the power to decide to spend the money and BUY
  Champion - 
  Primary Economic Buyer - 
  Influencers/Veto Power/Finance -
  
Ex. James B. and Brandon H. have an app development idea.  
Brandon has the idea, yet doesn't have the financing authority.
James has the authority, and is hesitant of buying.  
